WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:04.505
We can't use magic!

2
00:00:04.839 --> 00:00:05.923
What?

3
00:00:10.636 --> 00:00:11.721
It's true...

4
00:00:11.971 --> 00:00:13.514
What's going on?

5
00:00:16.642 --> 00:00:17.768
Something's coming.

6
00:00:18.853 --> 00:00:19.937
Get back!

7
00:00:30.156 --> 00:00:31.323
What is that?

8
00:00:44.211 --> 00:00:46.547
Huh...?! No resistance...?

9
00:00:54.054 --> 00:00:55.431
This many of them?!

10
00:00:57.016 --> 00:00:58.100
It's still no good.

11
00:01:06.108 --> 00:01:06.984
Ow!

12
00:01:24.460 --> 00:01:25.544
Ms. Kinera!

13
00:01:26.378 --> 00:01:27.463
Are you okay?

14
00:01:27.797 --> 00:01:29.548
I am. thank you.

15
00:01:30.466 --> 00:01:32.176
You used magic just now.

16
00:01:32.510 --> 00:01:34.094
But it wasn't fully formed.

17
00:01:34.845 --> 00:01:38.433
Something near the school building
seems to be canceling it out.

18
00:01:38.516 --> 00:01:41.977
I would say those shadow wolves
have something to do with it.

19
00:01:42.228 --> 00:01:46.065
I can't believe this is happening
right at the time the principal is away.

20
00:01:46.148 --> 00:01:47.733
What are we going to do?

21
00:01:49.151 --> 00:01:51.779
Normally. she'd just turn up on her own...

22
00:01:52.279 --> 00:01:56.242
Could you two please protect
the students in the dormitory.

23
00:01:56.367 --> 00:01:59.579
You and I will stay here
and stop the monsters from getting in.

24
00:01:59.662 --> 00:02:00.412
Okay.

25
00:02:00.663 --> 00:02:04.583
I'll go into the school with Master Beryl
to find out what's causing this.

26
00:02:06.794 --> 00:02:09.672
Only Ficelle and I
have the skills to fight in there...

27
00:02:11.257 --> 00:02:12.883
Guess we have no choice. then.

28
00:03:45.017 --> 00:03:45.852
EPISODE 3

29
00:03:45.935 --> 00:03:49.605
The Old Country Bumpkin
Sees Himself in an Old Man.

30
00:04:09.792 --> 00:04:11.168
They're everywhere in here!

31
00:04:12.544 --> 00:04:13.963
No time to rest. huh.

32
00:04:17.091 --> 00:04:19.093
It's okay. Ms. Kinera is out there.

33
00:04:31.355 --> 00:04:33.505
They're all coming
from the same direction.

34
00:04:38.153 --> 00:04:39.238
Over there. huh?

35
00:04:40.572 --> 00:04:43.409
Only senior institute staff
can go beyond this door.

36
00:04:43.534 --> 00:04:44.994
I think it leads underground.

37
00:04:54.378 --> 00:04:55.629
Let's go.
- Okay.

38
00:04:58.382 --> 00:05:00.092
Just how many of them are there?!

39
00:05:03.387 --> 00:05:06.557
Let's just focus on
holding things here for now.

40
00:05:13.731 --> 00:05:15.524
That's insane...

41
00:05:15.899 --> 00:05:18.360
Will the teachers be okay?

42
00:05:20.070 --> 00:05:21.822
So this is where all of you are.

43
00:05:22.281 --> 00:05:23.949
What on earth's going on?

44
00:05:24.867 --> 00:05:26.160
There's no need to worry.

45
00:05:26.452 --> 00:05:29.455
But whatever you do. don't go outside.

46
00:05:32.666 --> 00:05:34.543
Is everything really okay?

47
00:05:40.591 --> 00:05:42.802
What is that thing?!
- A monster!

48
00:05:42.885 --> 00:05:44.094
What's it doing here?!

49
00:07:45.132 --> 00:07:47.009
My presents...

50
00:07:52.306 --> 00:07:54.141
Let's take it down.
- What?!

51
00:07:54.224 --> 00:07:57.311
If it heads for the dorms.
all hell will break loose.

52
00:07:57.394 --> 00:07:59.104
That's true. but...

53
00:07:59.354 --> 00:08:00.731
It's too dangerous.

54
00:08:00.981 --> 00:08:02.232
I can't do it alone.

55
00:08:02.858 --> 00:08:04.193
But with the five of us...

56
00:08:04.693 --> 00:08:05.777
Let's do it!

57
00:08:06.028 --> 00:08:08.405
But how are we going to take it down?

58
00:08:20.792 --> 00:08:22.127
Master. there!

59
00:08:29.218 --> 00:08:31.053
What is this place?

60
00:08:31.428 --> 00:08:33.722
It might be Commander Lucy's laboratory.

61
00:08:34.848 --> 00:08:37.893
So this is where
she develops her magic?

62
00:08:42.481 --> 00:08:43.690
Vice Principal Brown?

63
00:08:45.192 --> 00:08:46.443
Oh. it's you two.

64
00:08:46.610 --> 00:08:48.195
What happened?

65
00:08:48.445 --> 00:08:52.324
That damn principal...
She was hiding something unthinkable.

66
00:08:53.909 --> 00:08:58.121
There was a powerful seal
on that room there.

67
00:08:58.789 --> 00:09:03.001
If there was a secret behind
her eternal youth. it had to be here...

68
00:09:03.710 --> 00:09:05.295
That's what I thought.

69
00:09:06.755 --> 00:09:07.798
Eternal youth...

70
00:09:08.423 --> 00:09:12.094
I spent years researching
how to break the seal. but I couldn't.

71
00:09:12.427 --> 00:09:17.724
So I had to create a magical accessory
that cancels all magic indiscriminately.

72
00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:21.478
But there was no such secret after all.

73
00:09:21.728 --> 00:09:23.855
And then the monsters emerged.

74
00:09:24.523 --> 00:09:26.817
That's why we couldn't use magic.

75
00:09:27.192 --> 00:09:28.694
Where's the magical accessory?

76
00:09:28.777 --> 00:09:32.698
In the classroom
on the first floor. directly above us.

77
00:09:32.948 --> 00:09:35.117
Master. I'll handle the magical accessory.

78
00:09:37.619 --> 00:09:38.745
What's wrong?

79
00:09:39.997 --> 00:09:41.665
Leave him to me. too.

80
00:09:41.915 --> 00:09:44.251
I'll take him to
the healing magic teacher.

81
00:09:44.418 --> 00:09:45.168
Thanks.

82
00:09:45.544 --> 00:09:46.545
Can you stand?

83
00:09:48.547 --> 00:09:50.674
If I were younger

84
00:09:50.757 --> 00:09:53.385
and a more powerful wizard.

85
00:09:53.552 --> 00:09:55.679
I wouldn't lose to monsters like that!

86
00:09:57.014 --> 00:09:59.266
The fear of growing old...

87
00:10:02.227 --> 00:10:04.563
You two just wouldn't understand.

88
00:10:30.130 --> 00:10:31.256
This is...

89
00:10:35.218 --> 00:10:38.764
These knives are short. but we can
probably use sword magic with them.

90
00:10:39.222 --> 00:10:40.640
It's worth a try!

91
00:10:41.058 --> 00:10:43.560
This is what we've been studying for!

92
00:10:54.321 --> 00:10:57.282
So I guess this won't end
until I take this thing down...

93
00:11:04.790 --> 00:11:08.502
That helps. If it's chained up.
it shouldn't be able to go berserk... huh?

94
00:11:09.169 --> 00:11:11.254
Hey. hey. cut it out!

95
00:11:27.521 --> 00:11:29.815
The boss monster's tough.

96
00:11:39.991 --> 00:11:42.369
If it's unleashed...

97
00:11:44.871 --> 00:11:46.998
Mewi and the others are upstairs!

98
00:11:59.761 --> 00:12:01.430
It's got flying projectiles too?!

99
00:12:18.864 --> 00:12:21.199
Things just got messy here...

100
00:12:25.078 --> 00:12:26.329
Haah!

101
00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:28.957
Yah!

102
00:12:29.249 --> 00:12:30.375
Hrgh!

103
00:12:30.792 --> 00:12:31.918
Hah!

104
00:12:49.352 --> 00:12:51.521
We can't do it like Miss Ficelle.

105
00:12:51.771 --> 00:12:53.273
What are we gonna do. then?

106
00:12:54.232 --> 00:12:55.650
I've got an idea.

107
00:13:05.243 --> 00:13:06.661
Sorry for the wait. Master.

108
00:13:11.625 --> 00:13:13.725
Thanks for that.
How's the vice principal?

109
00:13:14.294 --> 00:13:16.922
He's okay.
I destroyed the magical accessory too.

110
00:13:17.631 --> 00:13:18.715
Be careful!

111
00:13:43.865 --> 00:13:45.075
It looks strong...

112
00:13:45.325 --> 00:13:49.412
Master. I'm going to fortify my magic
so I can take it down with one strike.

113
00:13:49.788 --> 00:13:52.082
Can you cover me while I do?

114
00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:53.208
Got it.

115
00:13:58.755 --> 00:14:00.507
What does she mean. "fortify"?

116
00:14:00.924 --> 00:14:02.759
I don't really get it. but anyway...

117
00:14:03.802 --> 00:14:04.928
Over here!

118
00:14:15.021 --> 00:14:16.189
Now!

119
00:14:34.374 --> 00:14:35.542
Now!

120
00:14:58.815 --> 00:15:00.025
We did it.

121
00:15:19.711 --> 00:15:20.837
She's still not done?

122
00:15:32.515 --> 00:15:34.142
Hurry up. would you. Ficelle!

123
00:15:55.288 --> 00:15:56.206
That was close!

124
00:15:56.289 --> 00:15:57.374
Focus.

125
00:16:09.928 --> 00:16:11.554
Guess I'm getting old too.

126
00:16:26.486 --> 00:16:27.529
Master!

127
00:16:29.114 --> 00:16:30.198
Secret Blade...

128
00:16:30.990 --> 00:16:32.200
Curtana!

129
00:16:54.139 --> 00:16:55.390
What's that?

130
00:16:56.307 --> 00:16:57.851
It's giving me a bad feeling.

131
00:17:04.149 --> 00:17:05.442
What's happening?

132
00:17:05.984 --> 00:17:07.402
It's trying to re-form.

133
00:17:17.287 --> 00:17:19.080
It... split...

134
00:17:19.289 --> 00:17:21.040
The bad feeling is gone.

135
00:17:21.833 --> 00:17:23.794
You did great.

136
00:17:23.877 --> 00:17:25.712
But still. "Secret Blade"?

137
00:17:26.421 --> 00:17:29.549
The commander named it. not me.

138
00:17:29.966 --> 00:17:32.343
But you said it.
so that means you like it.

139
00:17:33.386 --> 00:17:34.137
Yeah...

140
00:17:34.220 --> 00:17:35.764
Then there's no problem.

141
00:17:35.847 --> 00:17:38.141
I think "Secret Blade" is cool.

142
00:17:39.851 --> 00:17:43.396
Ow. ow. ow. that hurts. Ficelle!

143
00:17:45.273 --> 00:17:48.985
For an old guy like me. "secret blade"
would be too embarrassing to say.

144
00:17:50.987 --> 00:17:54.157
Your plan was a great success. Mewi.

145
00:17:54.741 --> 00:17:58.286
I can't believe
you came up with using the tablecloth.

146
00:17:59.579 --> 00:18:02.415
My magic flame dies out quickly.

147
00:18:02.749 --> 00:18:05.399
But once I light something with it.
it keeps burning.

148
00:18:06.795 --> 00:18:09.589
Throwing knives directly
is also an option.

149
00:18:09.881 --> 00:18:14.636
Miss Ficelle said we should use
whatever we could in a fight.

150
00:18:16.971 --> 00:18:21.893
Mewi. thanks for helping me out earlier
when things got dangerous.

151
00:18:26.606 --> 00:18:29.025
Yeah. well... we're friends.

152
00:18:32.445 --> 00:18:35.073
I'm kinda hungry.
- Me too!

153
00:18:35.156 --> 00:18:37.117
You just ate!

154
00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:39.286
Moving around like that makes you hungry!

155
00:18:39.369 --> 00:18:40.787
We worked hard. after all.

156
00:18:40.912 --> 00:18:43.706
Just a bit more.
and we can clean all this up.

157
00:18:44.791 --> 00:18:46.543
One. two...

158
00:18:47.126 --> 00:18:48.920
One. two...

159
00:18:49.420 --> 00:18:51.339
One. two...

160
00:18:51.756 --> 00:18:53.508
One. two...

161
00:18:54.092 --> 00:18:55.593
One. two...

162
00:18:56.427 --> 00:18:58.096
One. two...

163
00:18:58.721 --> 00:19:00.598
One. two...

164
00:19:00.765 --> 00:19:02.600
One. two...

165
00:19:03.977 --> 00:19:06.646
Your right hand goes here.
and your left hand. here.

166
00:19:09.232 --> 00:19:11.651
That's better.
You catch on quickly.

167
00:19:12.694 --> 00:19:14.404
One. two...

168
00:19:15.697 --> 00:19:17.574
Fice has changed.

169
00:19:17.907 --> 00:19:20.243
Yeah. So have Mewi and the others.

170
00:19:20.743 --> 00:19:22.537
The class is a big hit too.

171
00:19:22.662 --> 00:19:25.665
Ficelle's actions in what happened
caused quite a stir.

172
00:19:26.082 --> 00:19:29.961
Still. you really had your work
cut out for you this time. Beryl.

173
00:19:30.461 --> 00:19:33.631
Yeah. I really gave it my all.

174
00:19:33.882 --> 00:19:35.758
You were away on business. after all.

175
00:19:36.342 --> 00:19:39.429
So what was that thing down there?

176
00:19:40.471 --> 00:19:44.267
Lono Ambrosia. A named monster.

177
00:19:44.809 --> 00:19:47.937
I hid it down there to seal it away.
and for research.

178
00:19:48.813 --> 00:19:51.691
I really wish
you wouldn't hide things like that.

179
00:19:51.983 --> 00:19:55.821
I didn't have much choice.
Even I can't destroy its core.

180
00:19:55.904 --> 00:19:57.197
Huh?!
- What?

181
00:19:57.280 --> 00:20:00.366
Well...
- If you've got something to say. say it.

182
00:20:00.992 --> 00:20:02.201
The core...

183
00:20:04.120 --> 00:20:05.288
You mean this?

184
00:20:05.830 --> 00:20:08.082
What?! You split it in two?

185
00:20:10.293 --> 00:20:12.337
You really are amazing.

186
00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:14.047
No. what's amazing...

187
00:20:16.090 --> 00:20:17.300
is this.

188
00:20:19.093 --> 00:20:20.511
How's Vice Principal Brown?

189
00:20:20.803 --> 00:20:23.806
Thanks to healing magic. he's recovering.

190
00:20:24.557 --> 00:20:28.895
Of course.
he can't just be let off scot-free.

191
00:20:29.145 --> 00:20:30.396
I figured as much...

192
00:20:32.482 --> 00:20:36.778
Thinking he could surpass me
with the secret of eternal youth...

193
00:20:37.695 --> 00:20:39.155
That upstart.

194
00:20:39.697 --> 00:20:44.577
What matters is striving to improve
through mutual effort and sincerity.

195
00:20:45.411 --> 00:20:47.622
He used to do that.

196
00:20:48.206 --> 00:20:53.211
That's why he stood beside me as one of
the two pillars of the Magic Corps.

197
00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:06.057
The fear of growing old...

198
00:21:07.225 --> 00:21:09.560
You two just wouldn't understand.

199
00:21:10.895 --> 00:21:12.689
No. I do understand.

200
00:21:13.815 --> 00:21:15.900
One day. I'll lay down my sword.

201
00:21:18.277 --> 00:21:20.822
And when that day comes. I...

202
00:22:54.957 --> 00:22:58.586
It's hard to take the last morsel
from a shared platter.

203
00:22:59.212 --> 00:23:03.174
But I want to be the kind of brave old guy
who dares to eat it anyway.

204
00:23:04.300 --> 00:23:07.429
Next time: "The Old Country Bumpkin
Returns Home."

205
00:23:07.512 --> 00:23:08.888
SUBTITLES BY: MARDI MIYAKE
